Sinovel Wind Unit to Invest $30 Million in Huaneng Renewables Initial Sale

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-05-29T10:27:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/sinovel-wind-unit-to-invest-30-million-in-huaneng-renewables-initial-sale.html
Sinovel Wind Group Co.’s unit plans
to buy up to $30 million worth of shares in the Hong Kong
initial public offering of Huaneng Renewables Corp., the wind
unit of  China ’s biggest power producer, according to a statement
to the  Shanghai Stock Exchange  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
